<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 chuán dào shì zhǔ de mìng lìng méi yǒu lǐ yóu bù tīng cóng
 chuán fú yīn wǒ men zé wú páng dài yī dìng chuán huí yé lù sā lěng
 yīn wèi mén kǒng shēn jìn shòu shāng de shǒu shí shí gǎn dòng měi kē zhōng guó xīn
 miàn duì fēng yǔ jǔ qǐ jiān qiáng shǒu bì shèng líng cuī cù wǒ men qù
 shén fù yǔ wǒ men yī shuāng zú shì ràng wǒ men xiàng qián jìn
 suǒ yǐ wǒ men bù néng tíng liú yī dìng yào chuán huí qù</lyrics>
